{"tid":1200704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NY Times 美國嚴重關注香港引渡法的擬議修正案","createTime":"2019-06-10T20:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T00:10:53.000Z","uid":111884,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f26d023ee4b1a9708a8285fc20501a8af2888331","tid":1200704,"uid":111884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:55:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>U.S. Gravely Concerned by Proposed Amendments to Hong Kong Extradition Laws</strong><br />\n<br />\nWASHINGTON &mdash; The United States is gravely concerned about proposed amendments to Hong Kong laws that would allow suspects to be extradited to mainland China, a U.S. State Department spokeswoman said on Monday.<br />\n<br />\nMorgan Ortagus told a regular news briefing that &quot;the continued erosion of the 'one country, two systems' framework puts at risk Hong Kong's long-established special status in international affairs.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2019/06/10/world/asia/10reuters-hongkong-extradition-usa.html?searchResultPosition=9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Freuters%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2Fworld%2Fasia%2F10reuters-hongkong-extradition-usa.html%3FsearchResultPosition%3D9&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=5921e5e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2019/06/10/world/asia/10reuters-hongkong-extradition-usa.html?searchResultPosition=9</a>"},{"pid":"2a4a63fe4e5fb4290d205f43f9043947bbc45180","tid":1200704,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:59:14.000Z","msg":"姐係仲傾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美帝方面仲有機"},{"pid":"25f844e5d9f1614480d85530cca92738cc039403","tid":1200704,"uid":111884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3kv5Su.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3kv